# SCSS Styling Guidelines

Styling conventions and patterns for this project.

---

## 1. File Organization

### File Naming
- Match component: `VMDetails.tsx` → `vm-details.scss`
- Lowercase kebab-case
- Place in same directory as component

### File Structure
```scss
// 1. Variables (if component-specific)
$vm-details-header-height: 60px;

// 2. Main block
.vm-details {
  // Layout
  // Spacing
  // Typography
  // Colors
  
  // 3. Elements (BEM)
  &__header { }
  &__content { }
  &__footer { }
  
  // 4. Modifiers (BEM)
  &--loading { }
  &--compact { }
  
  // 5. States
  &:hover { }
  &:focus { }
  
  // 6. Responsive
  @media (max-width: 768px) { }
}
```

