## 2. BEM Methodology

### Block
- Component's root class
- Lowercase kebab-case
- Unique, descriptive name

### Element
- Child parts of block
- Double underscore separator: `&__element`
- Describes purpose, not appearance

### Modifier
- Variations of block/element
- Double hyphen separator: `&--modifier`
- Describes state or variant

### Examples
```scss
// Block
.vm-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  
  // Elements
  &__header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  
  &__item {
    padding: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--pf-v6-global--BorderColor--100);
  }
  
  &__empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--xl);
  }
  
  // Modifiers
  &--compact {
    .vm-list__item {
      padding: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--sm);
    }
  }
  
  &--loading {
    opacity: 0.6;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
}
```

