## 4. Layout Patterns

### Flexbox
```scss
.container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--md);
  
  &__row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--sm);
  }
}
```

### Grid
```scss
.grid-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--md);
}
```

### Sticky Header
```scss
.page-with-sticky-header {
  &__header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background-color: var(--pf-v6-global--BackgroundColor--100);
  }
  
  &__content {
    flex: 1;
    overflow: auto;
  }
}
```

