## 5. State Styles

### Loading State
```scss
.component {
  &--loading {
    opacity: 0.6;
    pointer-events: none;
    position: relative;
    
    &::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }
  }
}
```

### Disabled State
```scss
.component {
  &--disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    pointer-events: none;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
}
```

### Selected State
```scss
.list-item {
  &--selected {
    background-color: var(--pf-v6-global--BackgroundColor--200);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--pf-v6-global--primary-color--100);
  }
}
```

### Hover State
```scss
.clickable-item {
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
  
  &:hover {
    background-color: var(--pf-v6-global--BackgroundColor--200);
  }
  
  &:focus {
    outline: 2px solid var(--pf-v6-global--primary-color--100);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
}
```

