## 6. Responsive Design

### Breakpoints
```scss
// Mobile first approach
.component {
  // Mobile styles (default)
  padding: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--sm);
  
  // Tablet and up
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    padding: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--md);
  }
  
  // Desktop and up
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    padding: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--lg);
  }
}
```

