## 7. Best Practices

### Do
```scss
// ✅ Use PatternFly variables
padding: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--md);

// ✅ Use relative units
font-size: 1rem;
width: 100%;

// ✅ Use project-specific class names
.vm-list-item { }

// ✅ Use gap for spacing in flex/grid
display: flex;
gap: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--md);

// ✅ Use logical properties
margin-inline-start: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--sm);
padding-block: var(--pf-v6-global--spacer--md);
```

### Don't
```scss
// ❌ Don't use !important
.my-class {
  color: red !important;
}

// ❌ Don't target PatternFly classes
.pf-v6-c-button { }

// ❌ Don't use px for sizing
padding: 16px;

// ❌ Don't use hardcoded colors
color: #333333;

// ❌ Don't deeply nest (max 3 levels)
.a {
  .b {
    .c {
      .d { } // Too deep
    }
  }
}

// ❌ Don't use IDs for styling
#my-component { }
```

